reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Good product but..
reviews.reviewText: I Like that this product does not contain oils or soy and that it’s sourced from a natural beta carotene however, it only comes with 30 capsules per jar. I think it’s silly to order multiple bottles, we get a bit of a discount but it’s still too expensive. In fact a lot of this company’s products are too expensive. This will probably prevent me from being a continued customer, I will most likely look for an alternative unless this changes.
